NAME summarizer

INPUT task
  Text to summarize

INPUT length
  Target summary length (one-sentence, paragraph, page)
  DEFAULT paragraph

GOAL summarize -> summary
  Summarize the provided text to $length length.
  Preserve key facts, conclusions, and action items.
  Maintain the original tone.
  If the text contains data/numbers, keep the most significant ones.
  Output ONLY the summary.
